\f2\b \cf2 5. Information Gathered from Cookies and Other Similar Technologies
\f0\b0 \'a0\
PlushCare uses cookies and other similar technologies (such as pixels and advertising tags) to ensure the quality of your visit. In particular, PlushCare uses cookies to recognize users and their behaviors across our Services, streamline the login process, maintain a Member\'92s state while using our Services, and remember user-specific preferences. You can always set your browser not to accept cookies; however, you should be aware that in some cases, some of our Services may not function as a result.\'a0\'a0\
