\fs34\fsmilli17087 \cf2 You acknowledge that PlushCare uses session replay technologies, such as those provided by Quantum Metric and FullStory, that employ software code to record users\'92 interactions with the Services in a manner that allows us to watch and analyze visual reconstructions of those user sessions.\'a0
\f1\i The replays may include users\'92 clicks, mobile app touches, mouse movements, scrolls, and keystrokes/key touches during those sessions. These replays help us diagnose usability problems and identify areas for improvement. You can learn more about FullStory at\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.fullstory.com/legal/privacy-policy"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 https://www.fullstory.com/legal/privacy-policy}}\'a0and you can opt-out of session recording by FullStory at\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.fullstory.com/optout/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 https://www.fullstory.com/optout/}}.
\f0\i0 \'a0\'a0
\f1\i You can learn more about Quantum Metric, including opt out options, at\'a0{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.quantummetric.com/legal/privacy-policy/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 https://www.quantummetric.com/legal/privacy-policy/}}.
\f0\i0 \'a0\
