\f2\b \cf2 12. Links to Other Websites
\f6 \uc0\u8239 
\f0\b0 \'a0\
The Sites may contain links to other websites that have information we believe may be of interest to you. We do not endorse these websites. While we try to link only to websites that share our high standards and respect for privacy, we are not responsible for the content of the websites or privacy practices employed by other websites. We encourage you to read the privacy policy of each website you visit that may collect information or ask you to disclose Personal Information. This Privacy Policy does not apply to information collected on external websites that may be linked to or through the Sites.\'a0\
\'a0\

\f2\b 13. Cross-Border Transfers
\f0\b0 \'a0\
All of the information that you provide to PlushCare will be stored and processed in the United States. If you are accessing the Sites from other jurisdictions, please be advised that you are transferring your Personal Information to us in the United States where data protection and privacy laws may be less stringent than the laws of your country. BY USING THE SITES AND/OR THE SERVICES, YOU CONSENT TO THE TRANSFER AND USE OF YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION IN ACCORDANCE WITH THIS PRIVACY POLICY.\'a0\
\'a0\

\f2\b 14. Retention of Personal Information
\f6 \uc0\u8239 
\f0\b0 \'a0\
Except to the extent prohibited by law, and subject to this Privacy Policy, we will retain and use your Personal Information for as long as it is needed to provide you with the Services you have requested or access to the Sites and the Services, to document our business relationship with you, and as necessary to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.\'a0When determining how long we keep your information, we consider factors such as, but not limited to, the type and sensitivity of the data, the risk of unauthorized use, the purposes for processing, and the legal or business needs. Due to our data protection measures, residual copies of your information may temporarily remain in our backup systems before being automatically deleted or rendered inaccessible.\'a0\
\'a0\

\f2\b 15. Personal Information of Children
\f0\b0 \'a0\
This Service is neither directed to nor structured to attract children under the age of 13 years. Accordingly, we do not intend to collect Personal Information from anyone we know to be under 13 years of age. We will direct potential users under 13 years of age not to use the Service. If we determine that such information has been inadvertently collected on anyone under the age of 13, we will take the necessary steps to ensure that such information is deleted from our system\'92s database. If you are a parent or guardian and become aware that your child has provided us with information, please contact us using one of the methods specified below.\'a0\
\'a0\
Children between the ages of 13 and 17 are only permitted to use our Site and Services in accordance with our Terms and Privacy Policy, and only with the permission of their parent or guardian.\'a0\
\'a0\

\f2\b 16. Parents and Guardians of Minors
\f0\b0 \'a0\
We may collect personal information of your child in order to provide your child with our Services. Your consent is required for us to collect, use, and disclose your child\'92s personal information and we will be unable to provide your child with our Services without your consent. Your consent will be obtained via a verifiable consent form or other lawful mechanisms.\'a0\
\'a0\

